### Event Gateway API (port 5000)
### Use the VS Code REST Client extension: click "Send Request" above any block.

@gateway = http://localhost:5000

### Health
GET {{gateway}}/health

### Submit an event (CREDIT)
POST {{gateway}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-001",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z",
  "metadata": { "source": "mainframe-batch", "batchId": "B-9042" }
}

### Submit the same event again (idempotent: returns the original, 200)
POST {{gateway}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-001",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z"
}

### Submit a DEBIT for the same account
POST {{gateway}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-002",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "DEBIT",
  "amount": 40.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T15:30:00Z"
}

### Submit an out-of-order event (earlier timestamp, arrives later)
POST {{gateway}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-000",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 10.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T09:00:00Z"
}

### Validation failure: zero amount
POST {{gateway}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-bad-1",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 0,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z"
}

### Validation failure: unknown type
POST {{gateway}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-bad-2",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "TRANSFER",
  "amount": 10.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z"
}

### Get a single event by id
GET {{gateway}}/events/evt-001

### List events for an account (ordered by eventTimestamp)
GET {{gateway}}/events?account=acct-123

### Balance via the Gateway proxy (resilient call to the Account Service)
GET {{gateway}}/accounts/acct-123/balance
